Oakite Products Inc saidit intends to sell its personal care and beauty productbusiness, Paula Payne Inc.    Oakite said it plans to retain Paula Payne's warehousingand production facilities in Charlotte, N.C., for use by itsMlaire Manufacturing subsidiary. Paula Payne was acquired fromRiegel Textile in 1985 to expand Oakite's aerosol manufacturingand warehousing capabilities into the Southeast. Reuter&#3;